		<RichText x="1410" y="223" width="437" height="85" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「王」在原地对其攻击范围(3x3)造成<span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害，也常见于「王」连续进攻后施放。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="447" width="427" height="56" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">距离较远时，「王」直接使出3个「马」进攻，每次造成<span color="#ff9999">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="671" width="441" height="172" d:userLabel="仆↓人进行至多5段的普通攻击，其依次造成2" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「王」在C3~F6区域内召唤3个互不相连的孤「兵」，自身则<span textDecoration="underline">装甲</span><span>驾「车」连续进攻冲刺，每次造成</span><span color="#ff9999">90%</span><span>伤害；<br/>「兵」也会攻击自身3x3范围内的玩家，每次造成</span><span color="#ff9999">40%</span><span>伤害。「王」相撞3次后，装甲破损并损失</span><span color="#ffccbf">15%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffccbf">20%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffccbf">25%</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/门扉前的弈局1.assets/Image_26.png')" x="1393" y="137">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/门扉前的弈局1.assets/Image_27.png')" x="1392" y="361">
		</BitmapImage>
		<BitmapImage source="@Embed('/门扉前的弈局1.assets/Image_28.png')" x="1392" y="585">
		</BitmapImage>
		<RichText x="899" y="62" fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" fontStyle="normal" fontWeight="normal" color="#ad4218" width="207" height="28" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="1">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="造字工房悦圆 G0v1 常规体" fontSize="24" color="#ad4218">制图@Csxylic米游社</p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="66" y="1288" width="437" height="78" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.7490196078431373">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="16" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「象」：<span color="#ffacff">14雷</span><span>盾，属护盾，击破会扣除「王」</span><span color="#ffccbf">15%</span><span>生命值并瘫痪7s。<br/>装甲：3次特殊次数盾，「王」每击破一个「兵」扣1，击破会扣除「王」</span><span color="#ffccbf">15%</span><span>生命值并瘫痪7s。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="223" width="439" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「王」朝玩家方向进行至多3次的连续着棋，每次造成<span color="#ff9999">72%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="959" width="429" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「后」朝玩家方向对其近身范围以十字和X字形连续着棋2次，每次造成<span color="#ff9999">80%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="1410" y="1183" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「后」伸出双刃，朝玩家方向发动一次进攻，旋转的剑刃造成<span color="#ff9999">33%,33%,19.8%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="1183" width="418" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「后」在原地对其攻击范围(八个方向)造成<span color="#ff9999">100%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="1407" width="407" height="56" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「后」在原地召唤大量弹幕飞向我方，造成<span color="#ff9999">55%,27.5%,9.9%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="739" y="447" width="438" height="85" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「王」迅速驾「车」远离，而后召唤2个「车」进攻，造成<span color="#ff9999">75%</span><span>伤害；大概率补上3个「马」进攻，每次造成</span><span color="#ff9999">60%</span><span>伤害。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
		<RichText x="738" y="959" width="424" height="114" kerning="off" blendMode="normal" whiteSpaceCollapse="preserve" alpha="0.9019607843137255">
			<content>
				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「王」生命值达<span color="#ffccbf">6.25%</span><span>时，将立即召唤「后」援场，自身离场；直至「后」被击倒，低生命值的「王」才会再次出现并处于「将死」的低抗性状态。</span></p>
			</content>
		</RichText>
