				<p fontFamily="仓耳渔阳体 W03" fontSize="24" fontWeight="bold" color="#ffffff">「王」召唤<span textDecoration="underline">「象」</span><span>，并凌于其上，沿对角线移动，每次移动时「象」均进行落雷进攻，造成</span><span color="#ffacff">70%</span><span>伤害。「象」被破坏后「王」损失</span><span color="#ffccbf">15%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffccbf">20%</span><span>/</span><span color="#ffccbf">25%</span><span>生命值。</span></p>
			</content>
